            <div className="text-6xl mb-4 grayscale opacity-40">≡ƒò╕∩╕Å</div>
            <h3 className="text-xl font-black text-slate-800">Ch╞░a ─æß║╖t gß║ích m├│n n├áo hß║┐t!</h3>
